* Diagnostic Tools\nfor Performance
** DAG
***_ Visualizes execution plan
***_ Shows data flow
***_ Identifies bottlenecks
***_ Sequence of operations
** Spark UI
***_ Cluster → Spark UI
***_ Jobs, stages, tasks
***_ Resource consumption
***_ Timeline views
***_ Task distributions
** Query Profile
***_ SQL warehouse workloads
***_ Query History → profile
***_ Time spent per operator
***_ Rows processed
***_ Memory per operator
** Investigation Order
***_ Start with DAG (overview)
***_ Drill with Spark UI / profile
***_ Identify where time is spent
@endmindmap
